{"comments":"Stroke geometry atoms — line styling for borders, paths, and outlines.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nA stroke is the visible line drawn along a path or around a shape.\nThis module provides the GEOMETRIC atoms: how the line looks, connects,\nand terminates. For stroke DIMENSIONS (width), see `Dimension.Stroke`.\n\n## CSS vs SVG vs Canvas\n\nDifferent rendering targets have different capabilities:\n\n- **CSS borders**: Limited to 10 predefined styles\n- **SVG strokes**: Full dash patterns, caps, joins, miter limits\n- **Canvas**: Similar to SVG\n- **WebGPU**: Shader-based, unlimited flexibility\n\nThis module provides atoms that map to ALL targets where applicable.\n\n## Atoms Provided\n\n| Atom         | Values                               | CSS         | SVG           |\n|--------------|--------------------------------------|-------------|---------------|\n| StrokeStyle  | 10 CSS border styles                 | border-style| N/A           |\n| LineCap      | butt, round, square                  | N/A         | stroke-linecap|\n| LineJoin     | miter, round, bevel                  | implicit    | stroke-linejoin|\n| MiterLimit   | 1.0-100.0 (clamps)                   | N/A         | stroke-miterlimit|\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Stroke as Stroke\n\n-- CSS border\nborderStyle = Stroke.Dashed\n\n-- SVG/Canvas stroke\nlineCap = Stroke.CapRound\nlineJoin = Stroke.JoinBevel\nmiter = Stroke.miterLimit 4.0\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[129,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[129,3]},"title":"StyleNone"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[130,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[130,3]},"title":"StyleHidden"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[131,3]},"title":"StyleDotted"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[132,3]},"title":"StyleDashed"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[133,3]},"title":"StyleSolid"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[134,3]},"title":"StyleDouble"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[135,3]},"title":"StyleGroove"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[136,3]},"title":"StyleRidge"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[137,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[137,3]},"title":"StyleInset"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[138,3]},"title":"StyleOutset"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Stroke"],"StrokeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[140,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[140,1]},"title":"eqStrokeStyle"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Stroke"],"StrokeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[141,1]},"title":"ordStrokeStyle"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Stroke"],"StrokeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[153,44],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[143,1]},"title":"showStrokeStyle"}],"comments":"CSS border-style values (exhaustive enumeration)\n\nThese are the 10 CSS border styles. Each has specific rendering behavior:\n\n- **none**: No border, takes no space\n- **hidden**: No border, but takes space (table border conflict resolution)\n- **dotted**: Series of round dots\n- **dashed**: Series of square-ended dashes\n- **solid**: Single solid line\n- **double**: Two parallel solid lines\n- **groove**: 3D grooved effect (carved into surface)\n- **ridge**: 3D ridged effect (raised from surface)\n- **inset**: 3D inset effect (pressed into page)\n- **outset**: 3D outset effect (popping out of page)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"data","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[138,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[128,1]},"title":"StrokeStyle"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert stroke style to CSS string\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Stroke"],"StrokeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[156,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[156,1]},"title":"strokeStyleToCss"},{"children":[],"comments":"Parse stroke style from string\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Maybe"],"Maybe"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Stroke"],"StrokeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[170,53],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[170,1]},"title":"strokeStyleFromString"},{"children":[],"comments":"All stroke styles (for UI generation)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Stroke"],"StrokeStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[185,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[185,1]},"title":"allStrokeStyles"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[214,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[214,3]},"title":"CapButt"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[215,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Stroke.purs","start":[215,3]},"title":"CapRound"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"decl